Random seed	random_state = 42 (used for reproducibility in comparative runs)
Time budgets (AutoML)	Full: 180 s; Light: 60 s
Time budgets (Classic ML)	Full: 180 s (RandomizedSearchCV / extended training); Light: 60 s (fixed fast settings)
Time budgets (Deep Learning)	Full: 180 s; Light: 60 s (early stopping + epoch limits within budget)
Train/Test split	80/20 stratified split (seed=42)
Model selection	Validation-based selection inside training split (holdout or CV depending on framework)

 
