Table S15: Class distribution under alternative target formulations
Legend: The table reports the class distribution for the three target formulations used in the target sensitivity analysis: the primary binary disease absence/presence task, the ordinal three-class severity grouping, and the original five-class disease-severity target. Percentages were calculated within each target formulation.
